# QuickQuiz

QuickQuiz is a console-based quiz application developed for
INEW 2332 / ITSE 2359. The program presents multiple-choice
questions, validates user input, tracks scores, and allows
replay.

## Technologies
- Java (Eclipse IDE)
- C# (.NET, Visual Studio)

## How to Run (Java - Eclipse)
1. Open project in Eclipse
2. Run Main.java as Java Application
3. Follow prompts in the console

## How to Run (C# - Visual Studio)
1. Open solution in Visual Studio
2. Run Program.cs
3. Follow prompts in the console

